packets.name: VX-1 "Signature" (Right)
packets.author: n0shot
packets.description:
Color Rarity: !!Legendary!! 1/3

VX-1's are the very first shoe model designed by n0shot. This shoe color is the rarest of the first set, with only 3 pairs minted. It's also the only variant with a colored sole, ensuring you'll be seen, even while flying ;)
